Name: Fates of the Dragonborn
Author: litbeep
Description: Fates of the Dragonborn is a modlist intended to combine A Dragonborn's Fate with Skyrim Together Reborn, with a few extras thrown in. Some mods from ADF are excluded due to incompatibilities. Rootbuilder is used and included. See readme for installation instructions!

State.Name: Adamant - A Perk Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Adamant is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s perk trees designed to balance existing skills and add powerful new perks to the game.

State.Name: Aetherius - A Race Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Aetherius is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s human, elf, and beast races designed to balance the game’s races and add powerful new gameplay options.

State.Name: All Thieves Guild Jobs Concurrently
State.Author: JAKJ
State.Description: Lets you take on all seven types of Thieves Guild jobs at once, instead of only one from Delvin and one from Vex at a time.

Archives.Name: All Thieves Guild Jobs Concurrently - USSEP Patch.7z

State.Name: Alternate Start - Live Another Life - SSE
State.Author: Arthmoor
State.Description: Live Another Life provides an alternative means to start the game for those who do not wish to go through the lengthy intro sequence at Helgen.

State.Name: Apothecary - An Alchemy Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus and DeltaRider
State.Description: Apothecary is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s alchemy, food, and alcohol systems designed to balance existing options while adding powerful new effects to the game.

State.Name: Apothecary - An Alchemy Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus and DeltaRider
State.Description: Apothecary is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s alchemy, food, and alcohol systems designed to balance existing options while adding powerful new effects to the game.

State.Name: Arena - An Encounter Zone Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Arena is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s encounter zones designed to increase the game’s difficulty and provide an organic sense of progression.

State.Name: Better Third Person Selection - BTPS
State.Author: Shrimperator
State.Description:
SKSE DLL to overhaul 3rd person object selection. 



Rewrites Skyrim's crosshair selection to work more like true 3rd person RPGs - no more spending 5 minutes picking up tiny gold coins from the ground!

Archives.Name: Blade and Blunt - A Combat Overhaul-34549-2-0-1-1655589835.7z

State.Name: Blade and Blunt - A Combat Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Blade and Blunt is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s combat designed to increase the game’s difficulty and encourage active resource management.

State.Name: Blended Roads
State.Author: T4GTR43UM3R
State.Description:
Roadstones are blended to the ground mesh instead of assigning a texture to an extra mesh.

This eliminates a lot of road uvw issues.

State.Name: Cathedral Weathers and Seasons
State.Author: The Community
State.Description: A natural-fantasy weather mod.

State.Name: Cathedral Weathers and Seasons
State.Author: The Community
State.Description: A natural-fantasy weather mod.

State.Name: Cutting Room Floor - SSE
State.Author: Arthmoor
State.Description: A mod to restore several pieces of cut content in Skyrim Special Edition.

State.Name: Dynamic Mercenary Fees
State.Author: JaySerpa
State.Description: Simple mod that makes mercenaries ask for more or less money for their services depending on their level, your and their race and how good you are at bartering (your speech skill.)

State.Name: Enhanced Volumetric Lighting and Shadows (EVLaS)
State.Author: LonelyKitsuune
State.Description: SKSE plugin that improves volumetric lighting and shadows by synchronizing them with Skyrim's sun and moon(s)

Archives.Name: Hand to Hand - An Adamant Addon-59790-1-3-2-1656615942.7z

State.Name: Hand to Hand - An Adamant Addon
State.Author: Simon Magus - Colinswrath - Jelidity
State.Description: Hand to Hand is an addon for Adamant - A Perk Overhaul that merges Lockpicking and Pickpocketing into a single skill and adds a new perk tree for Hand to Hand combat.

State.Name: Lux
State.Author: GGUNIT
State.Description: Consistent and complete rework of Skyrim interiors lighting. This mod takes advantage of the latest developments in enb, including enb light, and has for main objective to offer a gaming experience as realistic as it is dramatic.

Archives.Name: Optional Lux Resource pack (No ENB light)-63588-1-5-1659114386.rar

State.Name: Lux Via
State.Author: GGUNIT
State.Description: Lux Via is reworking main roads while still focusing on lighting, adding consistent light sources between towns and villages, improving or reworking from scratch many bridges, crossroads and adding a lot of points of interest to make roads a bit more interesting.

State.Name: Manbeast - A Werewolf Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus and colinswrath
State.Description: Manbeast is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s Werewolf system designed to balance existing Werewolf mechanics and add powerful new lycanthropic abilities to the game.

State.Name: MCM Helper
State.Author: Parapets
State.Description: Simplifies the creation of Mod Configuration Menus and extends them with powerful new features, such as persistent INI settings and hotkey registration. Mod authors will be able to write simpler, cleaner Papyrus scripts for their configs. Players will be able to spend less time in menus.

State.Name: moreHUD SE
State.Author: Ahzaab
State.Description: Adds more information to the HUD about the currently targeted object and enemies.  Such as ingredients, weapon effects, potions, read books, v/w, enemy level, etc

State.Name: Mundus - A Standing Stone Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Mundus is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s Standing Stones designed to balance the game’s stone bonuses and add powerful new gameplay options.

State.Name: Mundus - A Standing Stone Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Mundus is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s Standing Stones designed to balance the game’s stone bonuses and add powerful new gameplay options.

State.Name: Mysticism - A Magic Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus
State.Description: Mysticism is an overhaul that fixes bugs in Vanilla spells, fills in gaps in the game's magic progression, and adds new spells from previous Elder Scrolls titles.

State.Name: PapyrusUtil SE - Modders Scripting Utility Functions
State.Author: exiledviper meh321
State.Description: An SKSE plugin adding several new scripts with native functions that provide various conveniences related to data storage and other misc functions to the scripter/modder.

State.Name: Pilgrim - A Religion Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus and Tate Taylor
State.Description: Pilgrim is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s religion system that adds dozens of new deities and with powerful shrine effects to the game.

State.Name: Quest Journal Limit Bug Fixer - Recover Disappeared Quests
State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: An utility to bring back quests that disappeared due to quest journal limit bug

State.Name: Quest NPCs Run
State.Author: Dispensation
State.Description: Makes slow walking quest NPCs run.

State.Name: Quests Are In Skyrim
State.Author: SarthesArai
State.Description: Makes radiant quest no longer send you to locations outside of the province of Skyrim.

Archives.Name: Realistic Conversations with natural social behaviors-1717-2-0.7z

State.Name: Realistic Conversations
State.Author: Gorgulla
State.Description: Every social logic in Skyrim for npcs is changed, they talk more often to each others. And will less likely greet to you from a distance, they will also greet less often too, making them to not act as much as robots. NPCs are also more clever and will know for example if they talked to a npc and will therefore talk to another or not talk at all.

State.Name: Scion - A Vampire Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus and rodvt
State.Description: Scion is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s Vampire system designed to balance existing Vampire mechanics and add powerful new vampiric abilities to the game.

State.Name: Security Overhaul SKSE - Add-ons
State.Author: kreiste-wSkeever-powerofthree
State.Description: Additional variant lock models for Security Overhaul SKSE - Lock Variations

State.Name: Security Overhaul SKSE - Lock Variations
State.Author: kreiste-wSkeever-powerofthree
State.Description: SKSE based framework for replacing overused lock model with unique lock variants.

State.Name: Security Overhaul SKSE - Regional Locks
State.Author: powerofthree - Kreiste - wSkeever
State.Description: Regional variant lock models for Security Overhaul SKSE - Lock Variations

State.Name: Sensible Bribes - Based on Speechcraft Not Level
State.Author: JaySerpa
State.Description: Bribes make no sense in vanilla, as the value mostly depends on your level, not your speechcraft. This mod fixes that.

State.Name: SkyUI
State.Author: SkyUI Team
State.Description: Elegant, PC-friendly interface mod with many advanced features.

State.Name: Static Mesh Improvement Mod - SMIM
State.Author: Brumbek
State.Description: A massive project to greatly improve the appearance of countless static 3D models in Skyrim. Basically, this is my attempt to make the Skyrim architecture, clutter, furniture, and landscaping much nicer.

State.Name: Tavern AI fix
State.Author: Andrelo
State.Description: Fixes couple of annoying things in tavern worker's behavior.

State.Name: Thaumaturgy - An Enchanting Overhaul
State.Author: Simon Magus - DeltaRider - Oreo - Hypebringer
State.Description: Thaumaturgy is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s enchanting system designed to balance existing enchantments and add powerful new weapon and armor enchantments to the game.

State.Name: Unofficial Skyrim Special Edition Patch
State.Author: Unofficial Patch Project Team
State.Description: A comprehensive bugfixing mod for The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim - Special Edition. The goal of the Unofficial Skyrim Special Edition Patch (aka USSEP) is to eventually fix every bug with Skyrim Special Edition not officially resolved by the developers to the limits of the Creation Kit and community-developed tools, in one easy-to-install package.

State.Name: Vanilla Script (micro)Optimizations
State.Author: Subhuman0100
State.Description: Rewriting many of the vanilla game scripts with the goal of increasing efficiency.  Replacing slower "convenience functions" with their faster native counterparts.    Re-ordering condition checks to implement "fail fast fail early" approach.  Cacheing of often-used values.

Archives.Name: Water Effects Brightness and Reflection Fix-63862-0-4-1648397849.7z

State.Name: Water Effects Brightness and Reflection Fix
State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: Fixes bright water effects at night and neon green reflections

State.Name: Water Mod - ENB Displacement Textures
State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: A light-weight water mod. Includes ENB-compatible displacement maps. An optional ESP only edits water records.

State.Name: Kezyma's Root Builder for Mod Organizer
State.Author: Kezyma
State.Description: Root Builder is a Mod Organizer 2 plugin that allows you to manage files in the base game folder through Mod Organizer, leaving your game folder in pristine, vanilla condition!

State.Name: Better Dialogue Controls
State.Author: ecirbaf
State.Description: Ever pick the wrong item in a dialogue with a NPC? This mod aims to fix some annoyances with the way keyboard and mouse selection works in the dialogue interface.

State.Name: Better MessageBox Controls
State.Author: ecirbaf
State.Description: Navigate all message boxes with the Left/Right and Activate (E) keys. Also fixes the clickable area of buttons so they are easier to select with the mouse.

State.Name: Bounty Preview
State.Author: Parapets
State.Description: Preview bounties before you take them and get the option to accept or decline them.

State.Name: JContainers SE
State.Author: silvericed
State.Description: Extends Skyrim SE Papyrus scripts (or SKSE/C++ plugins) with JSON based serializable data structures like arrays and maps. Embedded Lua interpreter.

State.Name: moreHUD SE - Settings Loader
State.Author: MaskedRPGFan
State.Description: Automatically loads the user config file of the "moreHUD SE" mod after you start NEW GAME or install this mod, so you don't have to spend time in MCM again with each new game. NO plugin.

State.Name: powerofthree's Papyrus Extender
State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: SKSE64 plugin that extends Papyrus script functionality, with over 275 new Papyrus functions, and 29 events.

State.Name: powerofthree's Tweaks
State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: Collection of engine bug fixes and tweaks. SKSE plugin.

State.Name: Quick Loot RE

State.Description: This mod adds a looting menu akin to the one present in FO4.

State.Name: ReCleaned Menu
State.Author: enzeinzen
State.Description: This is a very simple mod that removes some unnecessary buttons from Skyrim's menus. Say goodbye to unintentionally clicking on the mod manager or the Creation Club.

State.Name: Skyrim Together Reborn
State.Author: The Together Team
State.Description: Play Skyrim in co-op with your friends or strangers, complete quests, fight, explore the world.

State.Name: SkyUI SE - Flashing Savegames Fix
State.Author: SkyUI Team and ousnius
State.Description: Fixes the flashing savegame entries when trying to save or load a game in the in-game main menu (quest journal).

State.Description: Fixes the issue where SkyUI favourite groups may not equip correctly under certain circumstances, such as after upgrading items.

State.Name: Remove QuickSave Button from SkyUI System Menu
State.Author: uranreactor
State.Description:
This small mod removes the "Quick Save" button from System Menu (esc), that was added in SE.

You can now normally exit your game without scrolling in System Menu.

State.Name: Address Library for SKSE Plugins

State.Description: Contains header file and a database to make SKSE DLL plugins version independent easily.

State.Name: Bug Fixes SSE

State.Name: Combat Music Fix SKSE

State.Name: Crash Logger

State.Name: Encounter Zones Unlocked SE
State.Author: underthesky and z65536
State.Description: Prevents Skyrim from freezing the level of Encounter Zones (like dungeons) when they are first visited.

State.Name: Enhanced Volumetric Lighting and Shadows (EVLaS)

State.Description: SKSE plugin that improves volumetric lighting and shadows by synchronizing them with Skyrim's sun and moon(s)

State.Description: Displays your horse's stamina in the HUD when riding a horse.

State.Name: Noble Skyrim Mod HD-2K
State.Author: Shutt3r
State.Description: The aim of this mod is to give all of Skyrim's architecture a complete new look by changing its textures to custom ones. Beside the architecture, several other things, such as landscape, dungeons (ruins, mines, caves etc.), clutter stuff etc. have been re-textured as well, to match the rest of the mod.  Try it out !
